	</h2>
	<div
		class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr))] max-w-[800px] justify-center mx-auto gap-4"
	>
		<article
			class="border border-gray-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-center max-w-[254px] h-[242px] justify-self-center"
		>
			<h3 class="font-Baloo text-darkOrange text-3xl mb-4">01</h3>
			<p class="uppercase font-thin text-[19px]">
				Eres un emprendedor o creador de proyectos de habla hispana
			</p>
		</article>
		<article
			class="border border-gray-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-center max-w-[254px] h-[242px] justify-self-center"
		>
			<h3 class="font-Baloo text-darkOrange text-3xl mb-4">02</h3>
			<p class="uppercase font-thin text-[19px]">
				Estás listo para transformar tu emprendimiento al inglés
			</p>
		</article>
		<article
			class="border border-gray-600 rounded-xl p-8 text-center max-w-[254px] h-[242px] justify-self-center"
		>
			<h3 class="font-Baloo text-darkOrange text-3xl mb-4">03</h3>
			<p class="uppercase font-thin text-[19px]">
